CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 31, 1959, pg. B2 reads: State NAACP Convenes in 3-Day Meet Here - Local Branch Cited - Honorary local NAACP President Judge Homer S. Brown and the Rev. Charles H. Foggie, branch president, admire the Certificate of Merit awarded to the Pittsburgh chapter for outstanding work and accomplishments during the past year."
TitMainTitle: Judge Homer Brown and Reverend Charles Foggie holding Certificate of Merit award from the NAACP
